From: Oleksandr Natalenko <oleksandr@natalenko.name>
Subject: [pf-curated-6.3] cpu: x86 uarches Kconfig + syscall.tbl additions

Re-cut from natalenko's pf-kernel branch cpu-6.3 (tip d78811139a17)
as a single bulk diff, restricted to the files this overlay's curation
kept on the 6.3 (orphan/EOL) slot. Source: codeberg.org/pf-kernel/linux.

Combines uarches + syscall.tbl additions on 6.3.
